rview":"Ryōta Miyagi è sempre stato legato al basket grazie al fratello maggiore Sota, deceduto in un incidente in mare quando Ryōta era piccolo. Ora playmaker della squadra di basket della Shohoku, Ryōta si prepara con i suoi compagni a sfidare \"l'imbattibile\" Sannoh, il team campione del torneo nazionale."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"The First Slam Dunk","runtime":125,"tagline":"17 years and... 40 minutes.","homepage":"http://gkids.com/films/the-first-slam-dunk/","overview":"Shohoku's “speedster” and point guard, Ryota Miyagi, always plays with brains and lightning speed, running circles around his opponents while feigning composure. In his second year of high school, Ryota plays with the Shohoku High School basketball team along with Sakuragi, Rukawa, Akagi, and Mitsui as they take the stage at the Inter-High School National Championship. And now, they are on the brink of challenging the reigning champions, Sannoh Kogyo High School."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"灌篮高手","runtime":124,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://slamdunk-movie.jp/index.html","overview":"宫城良田、三井寿、流川枫、樱木花道和赤木刚宪终于站在全国大赛的赛场，代表湘北高中与日本最强球队山王工业展开激烈对决。面对强大的对手，湘北五人组没有退缩，在安西教练的指导下，他们抱着破釜沉舟的决心热血奋战，究竟湘北能否取得比赛的最终胜利？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"ただ、負けたくなかった。","homepage":"https://slamdunk-movie.jp","overview":"主将である赤木剛憲を筆頭に、宮城リョータ、桜木花道、流川楓、三井寿ら神奈川県立湘北高校バスケ部のメンバーたちは「全国制覇」を目標に掲げ、バスケと向き合っていく。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"더 퍼스트 슬램덩크","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"전국 제패를 꿈꾸는 북산고 농구부 5인방의 꿈과 열정, 멈추지 않는 도전을 그린 영화"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"灌籃高手 THE FIRST SLAM DUNK","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"「教練，我想打籃球！」火紅32年的經典漫畫《灌籃高手》從1990年連載到1996年，人物角色為了籃球比賽揮灑熱血汗水激勵不少人骨子裡的「籃球魂」，光在日本的發行量就超過1億2千萬冊，在台灣也擄獲不少粉絲，櫻木花道、流川楓、宮城良田、三井壽、赤木剛憲、赤木晴子等角色都各自有擁護者；儘管連載結束26年，書迷一直引頸期盼作品能回歸，2019年當原作井上雄彥在社群公佈櫻木花道的繪圖時，關注度瞬間破表，大家紛紛留言回憶起當年追漫畫跟動畫的感動，就知道書迷有多期待。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Коронный бросок. Фильм","runtime":124,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ханамичи Сакураги - хулиган, у которого долгое время не ладилось с девушками. Поступив в старшую школу Сёхоку, Ханамичи заинтересовался девушкой по имени Харуко, которая любит баскетбол."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"THE FIRST SLAM DUNK","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"SLAM DUNK 是日本漫畫家井上雄彥創作的少年漫畫，從1990年第42期到1996年第27期在集英社《週刊少年JUMP》連載。作品以高中籃球為題材，描繪選手們的人性成長，漫畫系列在日本國內的累計發行量超過1億2千萬冊。受此影響，越來越多的男孩和女孩開始打籃球，並製作了電視動畫（1993年10月至1996年3月）和遊戲等作品。2006年，為鼓勵年輕籃球運動員，設立「SLAM DUNK 獎學金」。2018年，發行全部封面重新繪製插畫，依故事段落重新分冊的新裝再編版（全20冊）。2020年，發行插畫集《PLUS/SLAM DUNK ILLUSTRATIONS 2》，迎來了連載30週年。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"เดอะ เฟิสต์ สแลมดังก์","runtime":124,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"มิยางิ เรียวตะ พอยต์การ์ดจ่ายความเร็วสูงของโชโฮคุ ที่มักจะเล่นด้วยมันสมองและความเร็วปานสายฟ้าแลบ ปั่นป่วนคู่ต่อสู้ด้วยความสุขุมรอบคอบ เรียวตะเกิดและเติบโตในโอกินาว่า มีพี่ชายที่แก่กว่าสามปี และได้ตามรอยพี่ชายของเขาซึ่งเป็นผู้เล่นท้องถิ่นที่มีชื่อเสียงตั้งแต่อายุยังน้อย เช่นเดียวกับพี่ชาย เรียวตะ ก็ชื่นชอบบาสเก็ตบอลเช่นกัน ในชั้นมัธยมศึกษาปีที่ 2 เรียวตะได้ร่วมทีมบาสเก็ตบอลของโรงเรียนมัธยมโชโฮคุ ร่วมกับซากุรางิ รุคาว่า อาคางิ และมิตซุย ขณะที่พวกเขาเข้าร่วมในการแข่งขันชิงแชมป์แห่งชาติระหว่างโรงเรียนมัธยมปลาย และตอนนี้พวกเขากำลังจะท้าทายแชมป์เก่าอย่างโรงเรียนเทคโนซังโน"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":124,"tagline":"17 anos e... 40 minutos.","homepage":"","overview":"Hanamichi Sakuragi é um delinquente com uma longa história de abandono por garotas. Depois de se matricular na Shohoku High School, Hanamichi se interessa por uma garota chamada Haruko, que adora basquete."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"The First Slam Dunk","runtime":124,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Le meneur de jeu de Shohoku, Ryota Miyagi, joue toujours intelligemment et à la vitesse de l'éclair, contournant ses adversaires tout en gardant son sang-froid. Né et élevé à Okinawa, Ryota avait un frère aîné de trois ans de plus. Sur les traces de ce dernier, joueur local célèbre dès son plus jeune âge, Ryota est également devenu accro au basket. En deuxième année de lycée, Ryota fait partie de l'équipe de basket-ball du lycée Shohoku, aux côtés de Sakuragi, Rukawa, Akagi et Mitsui, et participe au championnat national inter-lycées. À présent, ils sont sur le point de se mesurer aux champions en titre, les joueurs du lycée Sannoh Kogyo."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Cú Úp Rổ Đầu Tiên","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"“Người bảo vệ tốc độ” và người bảo vệ điểm của Shohoku, Ryota Miyagi, luôn chơi trí tuệ và tốc độ cực nhanh, chạy vòng quanh đối thủ trong khi giả vờ bình tĩnh. Vào năm thứ hai trung học, Ryota chơi với đội bóng rổ của trường trung học Shohoku cùng với Sakuragi, Rukawa, Akagi và Mitsui khi họ lên sân khấu tại Giải vô địch quốc gia liên trường trung học. Và bây giờ, họ đang trên đà thách thức các nhà đương kim vô địch, trường trung học Sannoh Kogyo."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Слем-данк. Фільм","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ханамічі Сакураги — хуліган, у якого довгий час не ладналося з дівчатами. Вступивши до старшої школи Сехоку, Ханамічі зацікавився дівчиною на ім’я Харуко, яка полюбляє баскетбол."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"The First Slam Dunk","runtime":124,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Al segon any de batxillerat, en Ryota es classifica per al campionat nacional amb l'equip de bàsquet de l'institut Shohoku junt amb els seus companys Sakuragi, Rukawa, Akagi i Mitsui. I ara ha arribat el moment de desafiar el vigent campió, l'Institut Sannoh Industrial."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"يعاني المراهق الياباني مياجي ريوتا بعد وفاة شقيقه الأكبر، ويسعى للبحث عن سبب لعيش الحياة خلال رحلته بمدرسته الثانوية، وممارسته لرياضة السلة ضمن الفريق الأساسي هناك."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"The First Slam Dunk","runtime":124,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ryota Miyagi jest szybkim jak błyskawica obrońcą liceum Shohoku. W koszykówkę zawsze gra z głową i werwą. Z wielkim opanowaniem prześlizguje się między przeciwnikami. Ryota urodził się i wychował w Okinawie. Miał starszego o trzy lata brata, który był znanym lokalnym graczem. Ryota, podążający śladami Soty, również zakochał się w koszykówce. Ryota chodzi do drugiej liceum. W drużynie Shohoku gra wraz z Sakuragim, Rukawą, Akagim i Mitsuim. Razem wezmą udział w Międzyszkolnych Krajowych Mistrzostwach. Staną twarzą w twarz z obecnymi mistrzami kraju, liceum Sannoh Kogyo.  (opis dystrybutora)"},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"灌篮高手","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"宫城良田、三井寿、流川枫、樱木花道和赤木刚宪终于站在全国大赛的赛场，代表湘北高中与日本最强球队山王工业展开激烈对决。面对强大的对手，湘北五人组没有退缩，在安西教练的指导下，他们抱着破釜沉舟的决心热血奋战，究竟湘北能否取得比赛的最终胜利？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"SG","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":124,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Shohokun lukion korisjoukkueen valon nopeudella kiitävä pelintekijä Ryota Miyagi panee vastustajien pään pyörälle. Okinawan saarilla syntynyt ja kasvanut Ryota seurasi isoveljensä koristossujen jäljissä kuumille kentille. Koripallosta tuli hänelle elämän sisältö ja sielu. Shohokun toista luokkaa käyvä Ryota ja hänen joukkuekaverinsa, heittävä laituri Sakuragi, kiituri Rukawa, donkkaava sentteri Akagi ja takamies Mitsui haastavat toistaiseksi voittamattoman Sannon Kogyon joukkueen uskomattomaan mestaruusotteluun."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":124,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"The First Slam Dunk volgt de scholier Ryota Miyagi, de pointguard van het basketbalteam van Shohoku High. Ryota speelt verstandig en snel, en met geveinsde kalmte probeert hij zijn tegenstanders te slim af te zijn. Geboren en getogen in Okinawa, treedt Ryota in de voetsporen van zijn oudere broer, Sota, die al vanaf jonge leeftijd een geliefde lokale basketbalspeler was, waardoor Ryota ook verslaafd raakte aan basketbal. Na het overlijden van Sota, wordt Ryota gemotiveerd om altijd door te zetten. Ryota en zijn teamgenoten Hanamichi Sakuragi, Takenori Akagi, Hisashi Mitsui, en Kaede Rukawa dagen hun gedoodverfde tegenstander, de Sannoh School, uit in de basketbalfinale tussen middelbare scholen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Slam Dunk: La Película","runtime":124,"tagline":"17 años y... 40 minutos.","homepage":"","overview":"Ryota Miyagi, un jugador inteligente y veloz, se une al equipo de baloncesto de Shohoku, donde compite junto a Sakuragi, Rukawa, Akagi y Mitsui en el campeonato nacional. Su próximo desafío: enfrentarse al campeón defensor, el instituto Sannoh Kogyo."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"The First Slam Dunk","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Szakuragi Hanamicsi egy link alak, akit régóta csak elhajtanak a lányok. Miután beiratkozik a Sohoku középiskolába, Hanamicsi érdeklődni kezd egy Haruko nevű lány iránt, aki imádja a kosárlabdát."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"The First Slam Dunk","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Efter att ha förlorat sin storebror brottas tonåringen Miyagi från Okinawa med frågor kring sitt eget värde och meningen med allt. All hans energi läggs på Shohoku High Scholl basketball, en sport Miyagi och hans bror kände samma passion för. Tillsammans med sina kompisar Sakuragi, Rukawa, Akagi och Mitsui ska han nu möta de regerande mästarna Sannoh Kogyo High School i The Inter-High School National Championship. Ska de klara utmaningen efter att de satt sin första slam dunk?"},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"The First Slam Dunk","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"סלאם דאנק","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"הסרט עוקב אחרי ריוטה מיאגי בן ה-17 שמתקשה להגשים את חלומו של אחיו הבכור המנוח להפוך לכוכב כדורסל במהלך משחק כדורסל גורלי שישנה את חייו וחיי חבריו לקבוצה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"The First Slam Dunk","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Geplagt von dem tragischen Verlust seines älteren Bruders kämpft Miyagi Ryota, ein Teenager aus Okinawa in Japan, mit Fragen nach dem Selbstwert und dem Sinn des Lebens, während er sich in Basketball vertieft – den Sport, für den er und sein Bruder eine gemeinsame Leidenschaft hegten. Ryota und seine Mannschaftskameraden von der Shohoku High School gelten als Außenseiter und nehmen es auf ihrer Suche nach Anerkennung und Ruhm tapfer mit einer viel talentierteren Mannschaft auf. Was erwartet sie nach ihrem ersten Slam Dunk im Kampf gegen den Abstieg?"},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"The First Slam Dunk","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Liceul Shohoku are meci cu neînvinsul liceu Sannoh, iar pivotul Ryota își rememorează parcursul greu care l-a adus în campionatul dintre licee."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Прво закуцавање","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Филм прати 17-годишњег Рјоту Мијагија док се бори да испуни сан свог покојног старијег брата да постане кошаркашка звезда током судбоносне кошаркашке утакмице која ће променити његов живот и животе његових саиграча."},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"},{"data":{"title":"The First Slam Dunk","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"O «veloz» e armador do Shohoku, Ryouta Miyagi, joga sempre com inteligência e rapidez, contornando os adversários enquanto finge estar calmo. Nascido e criado em Okinawa, Ryouta tinha um irmão três anos mais velho. Seguindo os passos do irmão mais velho, que era um jogador famoso na região desde jovem, Ryouta também se tornou viciado em basquetebol. No seu segundo ano do ensino secundário, Ryouta joga na equipa de basquetebol da Escola Secundária Shohoku, juntamente com Sakuragi, Rukawa, Akagi e Mitsui, enquanto eles sobem ao palco do Campeonato Nacional Interescolar. E agora, eles estão prestes a desafiar os atuais campeões, a Escola Secundária Sannoh Kogyo."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"6534fe662b210800ff849f78","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6534fe662b210800ff849f78","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$11","created_at":"2023-10-22T10:50:14.814Z","updated_at":"2023-10-22T10:50:14.934Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":6,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":569367,"adult":false,"title":"Night Shift","video":false,"overview":"Amy begins her first night shift in a hotel with a murderous past. Witnessing terrifying events and trapped within a loop, Amy must find a way to escape the flesh obsessed murderer and save residents of the hotel.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6141,"vote_count":31,"poster_path":"/9IqVWHddRBrlQQshIIeckEzEayI.jpg","release_date":"2018-09-07","vote_average":5.629,"backdrop_path":"/o3Dnwh9zCxx7uDvILfqAnPq59Jf.jpg","original_title":"Night Shift","original_language":"en"},{"id":606733,"adult":false,"title":"DU","video":false,"overview":"A persona inspired, close to Dogme95 ruled circular narrative. A young couple from the middle class avoids relationship issues and will rather discuss their first world problems in their minimalist architect cabin in Fjord Norway.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.184,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/dCsedR2jzu5RFDlvrBs3Fs159Ec.jpg","release_date":"2019-06-04","vote_average":4,"backdrop_path":"/wwqfwuN8f9hr838aaBtNNaiUQFR.jpg","original_title":"DU","original_language":"no"},{"id":997317,"adult":false,"title":"Kaguya-sama: Love Is War -The First Kiss That Never Ends-","video":false,"overview":"After pining for one another and plotting for so long, Kaguya Shinomiya and Miyuki Shirogane finally have their climactic first kiss. However, they struggle to define their relationship. After all, how much of their true selves have they really shown to one another?","genre_ids":[16,35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.4321,"vote_count":89,"poster_path":"/jY092qLqa7qTMelwRiNPpLUolEz.jpg","release_date":"2022-12-17","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/bCzkRouaqLUSpSP5KHuObo8Fam5.jpg","original_title":"かぐや様は告らせたい-ファーストキッスは終わらない-","original_language":"ja"},{"id":811948,"adult":false,"title":"Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - The Hashira Meeting Arc","video":true,"overview":"Tanjiro and Nezuko have been apprehended by the Demon Slayer Hashira, a group of extremely skilled swordfighters. Tanjiro undergoes trial for violating the Demon Slayer code, specifically smuggling Nezuko, a Demon, onto Mt. Natagumo. A recap of Kimetsu no Yaiba episodes 22–26, with new footage and special end credits.","genre_ids":[16,28,14,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.6266,"vote_count":256,"poster_path":"/j1FpReEQXp8JsgNQZcfGvzeXNoI.jpg","release_date":"2021-12-01","vote_average":7.018,"backdrop_path":"/daeD5T4MxFk5MppZlaNZoaK6lE9.jpg","original_title":"鬼滅の刃 柱合会議・蝶屋敷編","original_language":"ja"},{"id":783110,"adult":false,"title":"Smugglers","video":false,"overview":"During the 1970s, in Kunchon, there were women divers who were able to dive without equipment, including two best friends Choon-ja and Jin-sook, Jin-sook's brother and Hammer. They always collected seafood under water for living. But, as fewer factories started to be built near the beach, the women divers started to have trouble with what they were doing for living. Without any choice, the ship crews decided to join the smuggling business in the water to seek a way for their living. But the smuggling business in their village got too big for Jin-sook's family to handle and the peaceful village was gradually broken.","genre_ids":[80,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7242,"vote_count":72,"poster_path":"/j8Jx4vpBG258jPxd4o0kOLDwTvm.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-26","vote_average":6.535,"backdrop_path":"/vZaIAIX5XcXLsF4jRSp5x7wsRzn.jpg","original_title":"밀수","original_language":"ko"},{"id":2712,"adult":false,"title":"Jacob","video":false,"overview":"Isaac's son Jacob deprives his brother Esau of his birthright and has to flee for his life. He finds shelter with his uncle Laban, but is himself deceived. Finally, Jacob has to face both his uncle and brother.","genre_ids":[12,18,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.4141,"vote_count":54,"poster_path":"/bmwFf3fMgBKqtiST5sQ7wapeLFB.jpg","release_date":"1994-12-04","vote_average":6.556,"backdrop_path":"/rUIRJsgOFhWMcHIfjAmYSsfZUzk.jpg","original_title":"Jacob","original_language":"en"},{"id":1206577,"adult":false,"title":"Kyan Khojandi : Une bonne soirée","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[35,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0363,"vote_count":13,"poster_path":"/knlR2lydSYaeaAFLmRRb9Zb8gLU.jpg","release_date":"2023-11-17","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/us4AFdC5rh6qW6lHRB8NpaoxPte.jpg","original_title":"Kyan Khojandi : Une bonne soirée","original_language":"fr"},{"id":72808,"adult":false,"title":"The Flesh","video":false,"overview":"A piano player meets and falls in love with a beautiful and voluptuous woman who, by some strange procedure, leaves the man unable to move but with a permanent priapism.  After some time he becomes sick of it and she relieves his paralysis. Eventually she gets bored and decides to leave, but he can't take it because he loves her…","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9885,"vote_count":65,"poster_path":"/5s9UarEgQWXHtZbm8fakXQnveRt.jpg","release_date":"1991-05-09","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/UJje4GZglCtC8ZtYY8T4jj1RHm.jpg","original_title":"La carne","original_language":"it"},{"id":1229898,"adult":false,"title":"MoviePass, MovieCrash","video":false,"overview":"Exploring the company founding and the implosion of the business by outside investors who took over the company, left it bankrupt and under investigation.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4424,"vote_count":28,"poster_path":"/eWht9uFRrqmqnLDL5F9grwUiL62.jpg","release_date":"2024-03-09","vote_average":6.575,"backdrop_path":"/91LTJhQdL9F61ShXSxoKjtLUrfp.jpg","original_title":"MoviePass, MovieCrash","original_language":"en"},{"id":448337,"adult":false,"title":"Who Killed Cock Robin","video":false,"overview":"An ambitious journalist who witnessed a hit-and-run years ago reboots his investigation led by newly emerged clues. As he beats the clock to save the only survivor after her sudden disappearance, layers of unimaginable dark truths around a corrupted system start peeling.","genre_ids":[9648,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6302,"vote_count":83,"poster_path":"/a9qzcgV0w7U4BiYSAhMrB7h34m8.jpg","release_date":"2017-03-30","vote_average":6.964,"backdrop_path":"/p0JEbE5LiLpKqtq9P0pSQZdBex.jpg","original_title":"目擊者","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1095885,"adult":false,"title":"SHARE?","video":false,"overview":"A man awakens stripped of all of his possessions and trapped in a bare room. Aided by a primitive computer, he must learn to survive in his new isolated existence where entertainment is the only currency.","genre_ids":[53,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.577,"vote_count":22,"poster_path":"/9HZv3pcDFZDSl8pdzxohHQZa1y3.jpg","release_date":"2023-11-10","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/8siXo3LHPNW7ZCeM5YTIQnZLLKJ.jpg","original_title":"SHARE?","original_language":"en"},{"id":688900,"adult":false,"title":"Sol Levante","video":false,"overview":"A young warrior and her familiar search for the sacred place said to fulfill wishes. It's best not to anger the ancient guardians and spirits.","genre_ids":[16,28,878,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3466,"vote_count":59,"poster_path":"/pS1OpWvJAnSPytj7kDkxy9Y4pFf.jpg","release_date":"2020-04-02","vote_average":4.797,"backdrop_path":"/8yxePmKnk5XFQVo34Q8yab6BY5u.jpg","original_title":"ソル・レヴァンテ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":681303,"adult":false,"title":"My Fairy Troublemaker","video":false,"overview":"Violetta (337), a curious and cheeky fairy, gets lost in the human world. To find her way back to the fairy world, she teams up with the human girl Maxie (12) and discovers her true destiny.","genre_ids":[16,12,35,10751,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4558,"vote_count":39,"poster_path":"/wXsCtzppdU1SUvTtxznJyi9hiXv.jpg","release_date":"2022-10-13","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/p4o1xEIHdQVuchXzkFSQORh3gWx.jpg","original_title":"Meine Chaosfee & Ich","original_language":"de"},{"id":810406,"adult":false,"title":"2gether: The Movie","video":false,"overview":"To avoid unwanted attention, a college student asks the most popular guy on campus to pretend to date him — but their fake feelings become real love.","genre_ids":[10402,10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6572,"vote_count":36,"poster_path":"/iXsURq06m7NRzsvShjVHfWDmdAs.jpg","release_date":"2021-04-22","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/y2XkiVv21eIpRbYE5ML2yUt4mg5.jpg","original_title":"เพราะเราคู่กัน THE MOVIE","original_language":"th"},{"id":36272,"adult":false,"title":"Out of Reach","video":false,"overview":"Vietnam veteran Billy Ray Lancing, a former CSA agent who now works on a wildlife refuge in Northern Alaska, has been exchanging letters in a pen-pal relationship with Irina Morawska, a 13-year-old orphaned girl in Poland that he's helping out financially. When the letters suddenly stop coming, Billy heads to Poland to figure out why -- only to discover that the orphanage that Irina was staying in, which is financed by honest -- and unsuspecting -- good-intentioned Samaritans, is a cover for a human trafficking network.","genre_ids":[28,53,12,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.532,"vote_count":122,"poster_path":"/vhjIndW3ukB8tTegjUCYV8j4WBr.jpg","release_date":"2004-11-12","vote_average":4.5,"backdrop_path":"/yLDP5N4Z4w8S6uL4M5FQEBUJpaS.jpg","original_title":"Out of Reach","original_language":"en"},{"id":42341,"adult":false,"title":"Suspect X","video":false,"overview":"A male corpse is discovered with a smashed face and burned hands. Strangely, the cause of death is determined to be strangulation. When Detective Kaoru Utsumi attempts to corroborate the victim’s ex-wife’s alibi she discovers the mysterious neighbor and only a few small clues to help her disprove a seemingly \"airtight\" alibi...","genre_ids":[80,18,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.5